27a5ac756b32855949762825dc27ec7c8ea996","tid":185203,"uid":26037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T14:52:17.000Z","msg":"好似以前香港咁 唔俾茶錢唔救火<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f24776ca88743b1cbbfc40c2f8dbb3f0dd8535b","tid":185203,"uid":79553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:13:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>年薪43M, 計埋貪污 分成 應該有80M</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n年薪四億<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我建議你返小學讀讀數</blockquote><br />\nm=million</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nM係=million呀，咁所以呢？<br />\n<br />\n都係要返小學讀數呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最有趣係叫佢返去讀小學，仲有人幫佢解話，點計條數都係錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 連登幾多人小學未畢業<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40886a0563bae86b76d0f5c2e0ea194c0dff935e","tid":185203,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:34:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>消防唔係隸屬老解咩<br />\n消防戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家開始改革"},{"pid":"1bf5b7ae26b6f67bd07c0ea91e4b074551358922","tid":185203,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T15:39:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>消防唔係隸屬老解咩<br />\n消防戰士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家開始改革</blockquote><br />\n以前係用武警去救火<br />\n<br />\n但武警無救火既訓練, 所以經常去送死<br />\n<br />\n家陣開始搞專業既消防員制度"},{"pid":"61a8eaface2ec239af3ada7b998b28b924aef27f","tid":185203,"uid":32676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-03T17:12:58.000Z"